## Privacy & Telemetry

### Default: Zero Telemetry

No data sent to servers by default.

### Optional Telemetry (User Opt-In)

If enabled, upload **redacted counters only**:
- Rule count (number of active automations)
- Run count (successful executions)
- Error codes (aggregated, no details)
- Average duration (performance metrics)

**Never Collected:**
- Rule content or logic
- Entity data (tasks, events)
- User identifiable information
- Specific error messages

